				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4405707#post-3644648</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4405707/a-real-humdinger#post-3644648</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2017 03:58:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DrChandra</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1956625</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>@A Random Day: I'm aware that site veterans generally frown on gratuitous links to 'classic' articles, since it's basically coat-tail riding and straight up uncreative, but I thought it made sense in-universe for Fuller to do it since he wants scips that are already famous to minimize his own workload.</p> <p>While I'm posting I'll give a shout out to my beta readers <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/goodeveningdrwhite" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2297355&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="Goodeveningdrwhite" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2297355)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/goodeveningdrwhite" >Goodeveningdrwhite</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" >not_a_seagull</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebillith" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3042342&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="TheBillith" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3042342)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebillith" >TheBillith</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toastedraptor" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2988260&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="toastedraptor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2988260)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toastedraptor" >toastedraptor</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zachary-maxwell" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2975899&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1512273535" alt="Zachary Maxwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2975899)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zachary-maxwell" >Zachary Maxwell</a></span>.</p> <p>The feedback I got was more varied than I usually get, so I guess this tale has a good deal of Your Millage May Vary.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
